In the Matter of the Claim of Nicholas F. Moriello, Appellant. Martin P. Catherwood, as Industrial Commissioner, Respondent. Submitted June 1, 1964; decided June 4, 1964. Nicholas F. Moriello, pro se, for motion.

No one opposed.

*840Motion dismissed upon the ground that the determination sought to be reviewed involves a pure question of discretion of the type not reviewable by the Court of Appeals (Miranda v. City of New York, 10 N Y 2d 883).
